reviewText: Love Her and this show. Only Her videos are played though , I remember she use to play other artist videos and dog them ( with humor ) but now she plays her own in that spot instead. Still worth watching.
So fun to see the irrepressible Julie Brown again! Seller delivered fast.

Endlessly watchable, even without all the vids she'd gleefully skewer.  She fills some of the blanks with her own videos and footage from 'dare to be truthful' (fall-down funny - it deserves to be seen in its entirety).  Please Miss Julie, more volumes!
